-- pd.package: `emoji-list` and it's Usage
name: fifthtry.github.io/bling/emoji-list

`emoji-list` is a new conversation experince via using `FTD` lang:

To use `emoji-list` on your web package, add below into `FPM.ftd` file:

-- cb.code:
lang: ftd

\-- fpm.dependency: fifthtry.github.io/bling
\-- fpm.auto-import: fifthtry.github.io/bling/emoji-list





-- tf.markdown:

Once you add above lines into your web package, add `emoji-list` into your `.ftd` 
